lass=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math><semantics><mrow><mi>t</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">t</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.61508em;vertical-align:0em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathdefault\">t</span></span></span></span> （ <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math><semantics><mrow><mn>1</mn><mo>≤</mo><mi>t</mi><mo>≤</mo><mn>100</mn></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">1 \\le t \\le 100</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.78041em;vertical-align:-0.13597em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">1</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2777777777777778em;\"></span><span class=\"mrel\">≤</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2777777777777778em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.7719400000000001em;vertical-align:-0.13597em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathdefault\">t</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2777777777777778em;\"></span><span class=\"mrel\">≤</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2777777777777778em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.64444em;vertical-align:0em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">1</span><span class=\"mord\">0</span><span class=\"mord\">0</span></span></span></span> ）。</p>\n<p>每个测试用例只有一行，包含一个整数 <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math><semantics><mrow><mi>n</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">n</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.43056em;vertical-align:0em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathdefault\">n</span></span></span></span> （ <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math><seman